Reverse a String Using Recursion | Implement a recursive function to reverse a string. 

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "Chandu";
        System.out.println("Recursion Reverse string: "+ recursionReverseString(str));
    }
    public static String recursionReverseString(String str){
        if(str.length()==0) return "";
        return recursionReverseString(str.substring(1))+str.charAt(0);
    }
}

output:
Recursion Reverse string: udnahC
